🌱 EcoPulse AI – Sustainable Product Recommendation System

An AI-powered Sustainable Product Recommendation System that recommends environmentally friendly products based on user preferences, predicts carbon footprint, and provides sustainability insights using Machine Learning and Semantic Search.

📌 Project Overview

EcoPulse AI helps users discover sustainable alternatives to products by analyzing:

🌍 Carbon footprint
♻️ Sustainability score
🏷️ Product category
💰 Price
⭐ User preferences
🤖 AI-based semantic similarity

The system combines Machine Learning, Deep Learning embeddings, and FastAPI to provide intelligent product recommendations.

🚀 Features
✅ AI Recommendation Engine
Semantic product search using Sentence Transformers
FAISS similarity search
Personalized recommendations
Related product suggestions
✅ Carbon Footprint Prediction

Predicts environmental impact using a trained Machine Learning model.

Model:

Random Forest Regressor

Output:

Estimated Carbon Emission
Sustainability Analysis
✅ Sustainability Score

Calculates product sustainability based on

Carbon emission
Eco-friendly materials
Product category
Sustainability metrics
✅ Product Search

Search products by

Product Name
Category
Sustainability
Similar Products
✅ FastAPI Backend

REST APIs for

Product Recommendations
Product Search
Sustainability Prediction
Carbon Prediction
✅ Interactive Dashboard

Frontend includes

Product Cards
Recommendation Results
Sustainability Metrics
Carbon Emission Visualization
🧠 AI Models Used
1. Sentence Transformer

Used for semantic product understanding.

Purpose

Text Embeddings
Similar Product Search
2. FAISS

Facebook AI Similarity Search

Purpose

Fast nearest neighbor search
Large-scale recommendation
3. Random Forest Regression

Predicts

Carbon Footprint

Saved Model

carbon_credit_model.joblib
4. Sustainability Recommendation Model

Saved as

eco_model.joblib
